name: Star Wars Quotes
description:
Famous Star Wars Quotes from the films and TV Shows
 Please note that the author and Mue are not affiliated with Star Wars.
author: Alex Sparkes

quotes.quote: Try not. Do or do not. There is no try.

quotes.quote: Your eyes can deceive you; don’t trust them.

quotes.quote: The ability to speak does not make you intelligent.

quotes.quote: Train yourself to let go of everything you fear to lose.
quotes.author: Yoda

quotes.quote: Once you start down the dark path, forever will it dominate your destiny
quotes.author: Yoda

quotes.quote: Don’t call me a mindless philosopher, you overweight glob of grease.

quotes.quote: I find your lack of faith disturbing
quotes.author: Darth Vader

quotes.quote: You really have it bad for the Falcon, don’t you?

quotes.quote: May the force be with you, always
quotes.author: Obi-Wan Kenobi

quotes.quote: I got a bad feeling about this.
